description:
On today's episode, Jack Posobiec debunks Dr. Ibram X. Kendi’s entire life’s work, Jack gives you the latest news and information regarding the kickoff of the Kyle Rittenhouse Trial, Alec Baldwin faces the press with a bizarre statement, and 60 Minutes features a Transhumanist in its latest show.



Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
